27 23-99-1901. Definitions.
28 As used in this subchapter:
29 (1) "Crisis stabilization unit" means the same as defined in §
30 20-47-803;
31 (2)(A) "Health benefit plan" means any individual, blanket, or
32 group plan, policy, or contract for healthcare services issued or delivered
33 by a healthcare insurer in this state.
34 (B) "Health benefit plan" includes a nonfederal self-
35 funded governmental plan.
36 (C) "Health benefit plan" does not include a plan that
